{"id":671948,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":4,"day":4}],"page":"1","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"87","ytitle":"","mtitle":"这是共青团员们在烈士墓前宣誓","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1984\\04\\8444011601.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>清明前夕，本市各界人民，尤其是青少年，陆续来到龙华烈士陵园祭扫烈士墓，接受革命传统教育。这是共青团员们在烈士墓前宣誓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本报记者　臧志成摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>臧志成</FONT>"}]}